snippet.title: Hot Air! (Nitrome.com) Levels 1-5
snippet.description:
First 5 levels of the flash game Hot Air! from Nitrome.com, it consists of blowing a hot air balloon with a fan to guide it through the level avoiding spikes and enemies.
You can play it for free in your browser in: http://www.nitrome.com/games/hotair/?game=hotair#.X1oh8OdxdPY
I hope you like it!
